description:
I finally get around to starting the Level 1 storage area. It's going to be a big warehouse. All in all though, I only get around to building the inner ring of dispensers.

The idea I had for labeling the storage areas doesn't look or work as well as I was expecting. I decide to halt work on it until I get some feedback from my viewers.

At the end of the episode I (try my best) to explain some of the issues with playing music with an EATS road. It's possible to do, but you will have to sacrifice either tempo, rhythm, or flexibility in your songs.
